{{Infobox government agency |agency_name = Ministry of Economy of the Republic of Lithuania |type = [[Ministry (collective executive)|Ministry]] |nativename = Lietuvos Respublikos ūkio ministerija |nativename_a = |nativename_r = |logo = Ministry of Economy of the Republic of Lithuania logo.png |logo_width = |logo_caption = |seal = |seal_width = |seal_caption = |picture = Ministry of Economy of the Republic of Lithuania.jpg |picture_width = |picture_caption = |formed = {{Start date|1918|11|11}} |preceding1 = |preceding2 = <!-- (etc.) --> |dissolved = |superseding = |jurisdiction = |headquarters = [[Vilnius]], [[Lithuania]] |coordinates = |employees = |budget = |minister1_name = [[Virginijus Sinkevičius]] |minister1_pfo = |minister2_name = |minister2_pfo = <!-- (etc.) --> |deputyminister1_name = |deputyminister1_pfo = |deputyminister2_name = |deputyminister2_pfo = <!-- (etc.) --> |chief1_name = |chief1_position = |chief2_name = |chief2_position = <!-- (etc.) --> |agency_type = |parent_department = |parent_agency = |child1_agency = |child2_agency = <!-- (etc.) --> |keydocument1= <!-- (etc.) --> |website = {{URL|www.ukmin.lt/web/en}} |footnotes = |map = |map_width = |map_caption = }}
The '''Ministry of Economy of the Republic of Lithuania''' ({{lang-lt|Lietuvos Respublikos ūkio ministerija}}) is a [[government department]] of the Republic of [[Lithuania]]. Its operations are authorized by the [[Constitution of the Republic of Lithuania]], decrees issued by the [[President of Lithuania|president]] and [[Prime Minister of Lithuania|prime minister]], and laws passed by the [[Seimas]] (Parliament). Its mission is to develop positive legal and economic environment for economic development and ensure public welfare and employment.<ref>[http://www.ukmin.lt/en/about Ministry of Economy of the Republic of Lithuania]</ref>
The Ministry of Economy is responsible for handling government business in the following areas: business environment, export, innovation, state-owned enterprises (SOEs), EU support to business, public procurement and tourism.
== Minister == * 2008-2011: [[Dainius Kreivys]] (born 1970) * 2011-2012: [[Rimantas Žylius]] (born 1973) * 2012-2013: [[Birutė Vėsaitė]] (born 1951) * 2013-2016: [[Evaldas Gustas]] (born 1959) * 2016-2017: [[Mindaugas Sinkevičius]] (born 1984) * 2017-present: [[Virginijus Sinkevičius]] (born 1990)
